0to%20do%20this.%20Or%20else%20the%20money%20goes%20bye-bye.%20Get%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Skotnikova%2C%20Rinsch%20compared%20his%20situation%20to%20%26quot%3BBrewster's%20Millions%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%201985%20movie%20about%20a%20man%20who%20learns%20he%20received%20a%20%2430%20million%20windfall%20from%20a%20family%20member%20but%20must%20spend%20it%20all%20within%2030%20days.%20Skotnikova%20also%20testified%20Thursday%20about%20driving%20to%20meetings%20in%20Ferraris%20and%20Rolls-Royces%2C%20vehicles%20an%20FBI%20forensic%20accountant%20said%20Rinsch%20purchased%20using%20money%20that%20originally%20came%20from%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkotnikova%20said%20Friday%20that%20Rinsch%20tried%20to%20purchase%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20furniture%20from%20the%20French%20designer%20Jacques%20Adnet%2C%20which%20he%20considered%20%26quot%3Binteresting%20and%20underappreciated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERinsch%2C%20known%20for%20directing%20%26quot%3BRonin%2047%26quot%3B%20with%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-keanu-reeves-movies-ranked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Keanu%20Reeves%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bmonopoly%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20designer's%20furniture%20pieces%20so%20he%20could%20%26quot%3Bcontrol%20the%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Skotnikova%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spending%20spree%20also%20included%20over%20480%20food%20takeout%20orders%20on%20Postmates%20and%20Uber%20Eats%20in%20a%20six-month%20span%20in%202022.%20The%20FBI%20forensic%20accountant%20previously%20testified%20that%20Rinsch%20moved%20the%20funds%20from%20Netflix%20through%20different%20accounts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-director-carl-rinsch-options-trading-11-million-fraud-trial-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvested%20a%20portion%20of%20it%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20cryptocurrency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20spent%20other%20amounts%20on%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20personal%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294393095-a3e8-417e-bea5-961d20141ea5%5C%22%3E'Very%20special%20beds'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20Friday%2C%20jurors%20heard%20from%20Johan%20Ericsson%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20top%20H%C3%A4stens%20salesperson%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%20of%20the%20US.%20He%20said%20he%20met%20Rinsch%20in%202021%2C%20when%20the%20director%20went%20to%20the%20brand's%20Los%20Angeles%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERinsch%20purchased%20four%20mattresses%20for%20a%20total%20of%20%24617%2C610.66%2C%20records%20show.%20He%20received%20a%20discount%20because%20he%20bought%20floor%20models%20rather%20than%20having%20them%20individually%20handmade%20in%20Sweden%2C%20Ericsson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carl%20Rinsch%20with%20the%20cast%20of%20%26quot%3BRonin%2047%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6933478d04d0f0a114f18903%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223106%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20L%3A%20Ko%20Shibasaki%2C%20Hiroyuki%20Sanada%2C%20Keanu%20Reeves%2C%20Tadanobu%20Asano%2C%20Rinko%20Kikuchi%2C%20and%20Carl%20Rinsch%3Cp%3ETORU%20YAMANAKA%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20highlight%20was%20the%20Grand%20Vividus%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bblack%20shadow%26quot%3B%20colorway.%20It%20was%20the%20top-of-the-line%20model%20that%20took%20over%20700%20hours%20to%20make%2C%20Ericsson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Grand%20Vividus%20is%20not%20just%20a%20mattress%2C%20but%20a%20%26quot%3Bsleep%20instrument%26quot%3B%20that%20includes%20a%20base%20and%20leather%20headboard%2C%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bbed%20doctor%26quot%3B%20who%20visits%20your%20house%20to%20massage%20the%20mattress%2C%20according%20to%20Ericsson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERinsch%20was%20so%20pleased%20with%20it%20that%20he%20later%20modified%20his%20order%20to%20get%20an%20additional%20Grand%20Vividus%20mattress%20rather%20than%20three%20lesser%20H%C3%A4stens%20models%2C%20according%20to%20Ericsson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20two%20very%20special%20beds%2C%26quot%3B%20Ericsson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Jed%20Rakoff%2C%20who%20is%20overseeing%20the%20trial%2C%20chastised%20prosecutors%20for%20allowing%20Ericsson%20to%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20on%20the%20witness%20stand%20waxing%20lyrical%20about%20the%20qualities%20of%20H%C3%A4stens%20mattresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20going%20to%20call%20it%20a%20sales%20pitch%2C%20but%20he%20obviously%20deeply%20believes%20in%20the%20brilliance%20of%20these%20mattresses%2C%26quot%3B%20Rakoff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEricsson%20said%20that%20Rinsch%20never%20spoke%20with%20him%20about%20using%20the%20mattresses%20for%20the%20production%20of%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Horse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERinsch's%20defense%20lawyers%20say%20he's%20innocent%2C%20and%20the%20case%20is%20really%20about%20a%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20genius%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20challenges%20of%20the%20project%20and%20didn't%20get%20the%20support%20he%20needed%20from%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20deposition%20for%20a%20separate%20legal%20proceeding%2C%20which%20was%20entered%20into%20evidence%20in%20the%20criminal%20trial%2C%20Rinsch%20was%20asked%20why%20he%20purchased%20%26quot%3Ba%20mattress%20that%20costs%20%24450%2C000%20for%20this%20production.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20it%20retains%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinsch%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20a%20mattress%20that%20you%20spend%20%2430%2C000%20on%20is%20worth%20zilch%2C%20but%20a%20mattress%20that%20you%20spend%20%24450%2C000%20on%20%E2%80%94%20guess%20what%3F%20It's%20worth%20a%20hundred%20grand%20more%20now.%20So%20hey%2C%20what%20are%20you%20gonna%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20told%20Rakoff%20they%20expect%20to%20finish%20presenting%20their%20case%20on%20Monday.%20Rinsch%20%E2%80%94%20an%20engaged%2