%20to%20Netflix%20customers%20at%20a%20discount.%20A%20real%20bundle.%20A%20Netflix%20version%20of%20%26quot%3Bbasic%20cable%20%2B%20HBO.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20Netflix%20executives%20didn't%20actually%20say%20that%20on%20the%20call.%20Instead%2C%20we%20got%20commentary%20like%20this%2C%20from%20co-CEO%20Greg%20Peters%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20the%20HBO%20brand%20is%20very%20powerful%20for%20consumers.%20We%20think%20that%20the%20offering%20could%20constitute%20and%20would%20constitute%20part%20of%20our%20plans%20and%20how%20we%20structure%20those%20for%20consumers.%20And%20then%20that%20gives%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20options%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20do%20you%20package%20things%2C%20in%20different%20ways%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we're%20maximizing%20the%20value%20for%20consumers%20%2C%20and%20maximizing%20the%20value%20of%20the%20assets%20that%20we're%20then%20being%20able%20to%20present.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EShrug%20emoji.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sure%20Netflix%20will%20consider%20%3Cem%3Esome%3C%2Fem%3E%20tweaks%20beyond%20simply%20running%20two%20different%20services%20at%20the%20same%20time%20and%20selling%20a%20discounted%20bundle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%3A%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BMax%26quot%3B%20shows%20HBO%20Max%20has%20been%20making%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cheaper%2C%20high-volume%20series%20that%20were%20supposed%20to%20broaden%20HBO's%20audience%3F%20Do%20those%20migrate%20to%20Netflix%2C%20which%20already%20serves%20a%20much%20larger%2C%20more%20general-interest%20subscriber%20base%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20are%20tweaks.%20The%20big%20picture%20is%20that%20Netflix%20could%20operate%20Netflix%20and%20HBO%20as%20two%20separate%20services%20for%20quite%20a%20while%2C%20sold%20to%20overlapping%20but%20distinct%20audiences.%20Which%20is%20basically%20how%20things%20already%20work.%20Netflix%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269012147-53dd-4f11-be60-8c9331d257a5%5C%22%3EWhat's%20the%20opportunity%20for%20Netflix%2C%20and%20for%20HBO%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAntenna%2C%20the%20analytics%20firm%2C%20estimates%20that%2045%25%20of%20HBO's%20US%20subscribers%20already%20have%20Netflix%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%2015%25%20of%20Netflix%20subscribers%20also%20get%20HBO.%20That%20discrepancy%20is%20likely%20even%20wider%20outside%20the%20US%2C%20since%20Netflix%20is%20nearly%20global%20and%20HBO%20is%20still%20expanding%20internationally.%20Which%20means%20HBO%20could%20dramatically%20increase%20its%20reach%20simply%20by%20being%20attached%20to%20Netflix%20and%20its%20300%20million%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20worth%20remembering%20the%20original%20logic%20behind%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20%E2%80%94%20the%202022%20mashup%20of%20what%20used%20to%20be%20called%20Time%20Warner%20and%20Discovery%20Inc.%20The%20whole%20idea%20was%20scale%3A%20Put%20Discovery's%20cheap%20basic-cable%20fare%20in%20the%20same%20container%20as%20HBO's%20prestige%20hits%2C%20and%20you'd%20have%20one%20super-service%20that%20lots%20of%20people%20would%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDidn't%20work.%20HBO%20viewers%20wanted%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus%2C%26quot%3B%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FDr._Pimple_Popper_(TV_series)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epimple-popping%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20investors%20hated%20the%20amalgamation%20so%20much%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwbd-comcast-cable-tv-split-spin-sale-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWBD%20was%20preparing%20to%20break%20itself%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20deciding%20instead%20to%20sell%20to%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I'd%20be%20surprised%20if%20Netflix%20tries%20melting%20HBO%20into%20part%20of%20its%20giant%2C%20undifferentiated%20service.%20Much%20more%20likely%3A%20Turning%20it%20back%20into%20what%20it's%20always%20been%3A%20a%20premium%20channel%20you%20s