lix%20on%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWBD%20CFO%20Gunnar%20Wiedenfels%2C%20who%20will%20lead%20Discovery%20Global%20after%20it's%20spun%20off%20from%20the%20main%20company%2C%20said%20on%20the%20call%20that%20while%20the%20WBD%20as%20the%20world%20knows%20it%20would%20come%20to%20an%20end%2C%20he's%20excited%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20emotional%20day%2C%20I%20think%2C%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Wiedenfels%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea043699-2621-42e2-b0c4-44f06ee5d7a9%5C%22%3EWhat%20WBD%20execs%20said%20about%20the%20split%2C%20bidding%20war%2C%20and%20sale%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%20the%20call%2C%20Zaslav%20acknowledged%20that%20WBD%20and%20its%20employees%20had%20gone%20through%20a%20slew%20of%20changes%20since%20he%20engineered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-discovery-warner-media-create-new-streaming-giant-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emerger%20between%20WarnerMedia%20and%20Discovery%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20closed%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20end%2C%20we've%20gotten%20a%20lot%20more%20right%20than%20we've%20gotten%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Zaslav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWBD's%20stock%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20to%20nearly%20%2426%20per%20share%20since%20news%20of%20Paramount's%20interest%20in%20buying%20it%20broke%20in%20mid-September.%20However%2C%20WBD%20shares%20began%20trading%20at%20%2424.08%20in%20April%202022%20and%20closed%20at%20%2412.54%20before%20acquisition%20rumors%20heated%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WBD%20CEO%20reiterated%20on%20the%20call%20that%20the%20company%20had%20planned%20to%20split%20itself%20before%20Paramount%20expressed%20its%20interest%20with%20an%20unsolicited%20offer.%20Zaslav%20said%20that%2C%20as%20a%20public%20company%2C%20it%20was%20executives'%20duties%20to%20get%20the%20best%20possible%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20No.%201%20focus%20is%20to%20drive%20shareholder%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20Za