.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20dark%2C%20and%20the%20air%20boss%20overseeing%20the%20flight%20operations%20and%20landing%20signal%20officers%2C%20unaware%20that%20the%20cable%20had%20parted%2C%20thought%20the%20fighter's%20engine%20had%20ingested%20foreign%20object%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224681%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Nimitz-class%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Harry%20S.%20Truman%20(CVN%2075)%20conducts%20carrier%20qualifications%20in%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean.%20Truman%20is%20underway%2C%20carrying%20out%20routine%20operations%20that%20support%20the%20Navy's%20commitment%20to%20readiness%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20future%20fleet%20lethality.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6932cecc71107c9f345765bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223344%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20carrier%20Truman%20suffered%20multiple%20mishaps%20during%20its%20Middle%20East%20deployment.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%202nd%20Class%20Mike%20Shen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20was%20leaning%20left%20as%20it%20moved%20down%20the%20landing%20zone.%20%26quot%3BPOWER!%26quot%3B%20the%20lead%20LSO%20called.%20%26quot%3BROTATE%2C%20CLIMB!%26quot%3B%20The%20fighter%20jet%20was%20traveling%20too%20fast%20to%20stop%2C%20but%20not%20fast%20enough%20to%20take%20off.%20A%20back-up%20LSO%20realized%20the%20aircraft%20wasn't%20climbing%20and%20made%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEJECT%2C%20EJECT%2C%20EJECT!%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20called%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20rolled%20and%20then%20knife-edged%20at%2090%20degrees.%20Moments%20later%2C%20it%20plunged%20into%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bman%20overboard%26quot%3B%20call%20went%20out%20a%20minute%20after%20the%20plane%20first%20touched%20the%20deck.%20Sailors%20on%20the%20flight%20deck%20didn't%20see%20any%20parachutes%20deploy%20after%20their%20cockpit%20ejection%20amid