ked%20a%20washer%2C%20a%20small%20part%20that%20helps%20keep%20the%20system%20in%20place.%20That%20maintenance%20oversight%20ended%20with%20a%20jet%20in%20the%20water%20and%20two%20aviators%20overboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20this%20mechanism%20had%20been%20loosening%20for%20some%20time%20before%20the%20mishap%2C%20the%20investigation%20said.%20A%20missing%20washer%20could%20allow%20the%20pin%20in%20the%20arresting%20gear%20to%20work%20loose%20and%20shear%20off%2C%20ultimately%20causing%20internal%20parts%20in%20the%20gear%20to%20come%20apart%20under%20and%20the%20arresting%20cable%20to%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESailors%20across%20the%20board%20were%20poorly%20trained%2C%20the%20investigation%20determined%2C%20and%20a%20maintenance%20support%20sailor%20who%20was%20supposed%20to%20inspect%20the%20arresting%20cable%20and%20its%20mechanisms%20hadn't%20thoroughly%20done%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVice%20Adm.%20John%20Gumbleton%2C%20acting%20head%20of%20Fleet%20Forces%20Command%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20attached%20to%20the%20investigation%20that%20Truman's%20leadership%20across%20all%20levels%20%26quot%3Ballowed%20the%20air%20department's%20aircraft%20launch%20and%20recovery%20equipment%20maintenance%20program%20standards%20to%20decline%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20a%20critical%20point%20of%20failure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20May%206%20incident%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-aircraft-carrier-red-sea-cost-navy-millions-dollars-mishaps-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efourth%20major%20mishap%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Truman%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20its%20strike%20group%20suffered%20during%20the%20monthslong%20Middle%20East%20combat%20deployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20cruiser%20USS%20Gettysburg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-missile-cruiser-super-hornet-friendly-fire-incident-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emistakenly%20shot%20down%3C%2F